sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant Owner as Owner (AxonStore)
    participant Grantee
    participant AxonAPI as axon-api

    Note over Admin,AxonAPI: Step 1 — Initialise the store (once)
    Admin->>AxonAPI: init_store(base_path="/data/axon-store")
    AxonAPI-->>Admin: {status: "ok"}

    Note over Owner,AxonAPI: Step 2 — Owner creates a project and shares it
    Owner->>AxonAPI: POST /project/create {name: "research"}
    Owner->>AxonAPI: POST /shares/create {project: "research", grantee: "alice"}
    AxonAPI-->>Owner: {share_string: "axon:v1:...", key_id: "k42"}

    Note over Owner,Grantee: Step 3 — Owner sends share string to Grantee (out of band)
    Owner-->>Grantee: share_string (HMAC-signed, read-only)

    Note over Grantee,AxonAPI: Step 4 — Grantee mounts the shared project
    Grantee->>AxonAPI: POST /shares/redeem {share_string: "axon:v1:..."}
    AxonAPI-->>Grantee: {mount: "owner/research", status: "mounted"}

    Note over Grantee,AxonAPI: Step 5 — Grantee queries the shared knowledge
    Grantee->>AxonAPI: POST /project/switch {name: "@mounts"}
    Grantee->>AxonAPI: POST /search {query: "..."}
    AxonAPI-->>Grantee: [chunks from owner/research]

    Note over Owner,AxonAPI: Step 6 — Owner revokes access
    Owner->>AxonAPI: POST /shares/revoke {key_id: "k42"}
    AxonAPI-->>Owner: {status: "revoked"}
    Note over Grantee: Mount becomes inaccessible on next request
